column5: Anyone know how to contact Phil Rolfe,Walleye guide formally at Witch Bay Camp?

Last e-mail address I had was [email protected]. I don't know if he still lives in the Mercer, WI area since he was to re-marry when he left Witch Bay this summer. If that e-mail address doesn't prove successful, contact Gaill Hockett at Witch Bay, [email protected].
